			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="Repro steps:&#xD;&#xA;1. Start the game&#xD;&#xA;2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;3. Talk with Lorin. and skip the dialogue.&#xD;&#xA;4. SetGlobalOsirisFlag HAG_Hag_State_IsDead&#xD;&#xA;5. Talk with Lorin again.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;RECON  : SetGlobalOsirisFlag HAG_Hag_State_IsDead &#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;ACTION  :Talk with Lorin again." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="1016" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="This occurs if Lorin survived the fight with the hag. He is dazed and out of it. This is the victim who first say the player as a mind flayer and freaked out. &#xD;&#xA;1) In scenario one, he was never summoned by the hag&#xD;&#xA;2) He was summoned and attacked the player and saw the player turn into a mindflayer&#xD;&#xA;3) He was summoned and attacked the player but never saw the player as a mind flayer" />
